metadata.Plot: Maxwell Smart is called back to duty as KAOS is back causing trouble again, this time with a 'weather machine'. Although instructed to keep his mission secret from his wife, 99, Max can't keep hiding from her forever, and soon the two are working together again in this second Maxwell Smart movie.
